reviewText: Ive seen this on Qubo at my cousins house not in my house but I finally found it on DVD.

Great price for complete set of Shelldon. It contains CGI animation and is set near a tropical shoreline, both underwater and occasionally above water. The stories are partially educational, with a moral of the story segment at the end of every episode.

For the package.. all DVD stack together which have to be carefully putting in or getting the disc out
